<p class="border_p">You can put both uppercase and lowercase nucleotides characters and white characters (new lines, spaces). We were prepared for testing 3 sample DNA sequences, which were chosen specifically for the presented classifiers. Classifiers were trained on fixed length DNA sequences, hence it is required to note minimum length of the typing DNA sequence:
</p>
